"Click the clip icon to the left of the input field, or drag and drop files onto the input field. When dragging, the input field border highlights in the accent color to show the drop zone." = "点击输入框左侧的回形针图标，或将文件拖放到输入框上。拖动时，输入框边框会以强调色高亮以显示放置区域。";
"Clipboard Detection" = "剪贴板检测";
"Pasting (⌘V) is smart — Clarc detects what's in the clipboard and handles it automatically." = "粘贴 (⌘V) 很智能 — Clarc 会检测剪贴板中的内容并自动处理。";
"Image data (PNG/TIFF) → attached as an image" = "图片数据（PNG/TIFF）→ 作为图片附加";
"File path → attached as a file" = "文件路径 → 作为文件附加";
"URL → attached as a URL reference" = "URL → 作为 URL 引用附加";
"Long text (>2 KB) → converted to a text attachment" = "长文本（>2 KB）→ 转换为文本附件";
"Screenshots can be pasted directly — they are automatically attached as images." = "截图可直接粘贴 — 它们会自动作为图片附加。";
"@ File References" = "@ 文件引用";
"Type @ in the input field to open a project file search popup. Files are filtered in real time as you type." = "在输入框中输入 @ 即可打开项目文件搜索弹窗。随着你的输入，文件会实时筛选。";

// Shortcut Buttons
"What are Shortcut Buttons?" = "什么是快捷按钮？";
"Quick-access buttons shown at the top of the chat area. Run frequently used messages or shell commands with a single click." = "显示在对话区域顶部的快速访问按钮。一键运行常用消息或 shell 命令。";
"Adding a Shortcut" = "添加快捷按钮";
"Click the ⚡ button in the toolbar to open the Shortcut Manager, or press the + button on the right side of the shortcut bar. You can set a name, message/command, icon, and color." = "点击工具栏中的 ⚡ 按钮打开快捷按钮管理器，或按下快捷按钮栏右侧的 + 按钮。你可以设置名称、消息/命令、图标和颜色。";
"Terminal Command Mode" = "终端命令模式";
"Enable the \"Run as terminal command\" option to execute the shortcut as a shell command in the inspector terminal instead of sending it as a chat message. The project directory is used as the working directory." = "启用“作为终端命令运行”选项后，快捷按钮将在检查器终端中作为 shell 命令执行，而不是作为对话消息发送。项目目录会被用作工作目录。";
"Managing Shortcuts" = "管理快捷按钮";
"Open Settings → Shortcuts to reorder, edit, or delete shortcuts. Shortcut configurations are saved per project." = "打开设置 → 快捷按钮，即可重新排序、编辑或删除快捷按钮。快捷按钮配置按项目分别保存。";
"JSON import/export is supported for backing up or sharing your shortcut set." = "支持通过 JSON 导入/导出来备份或共享你的快捷按钮集合。";

// Inspector Panel
"Opening the Inspector Panel" = "打开检查器面板";
"Click the sidebar.trailing (⊟) button at the top right of the toolbar to toggle the inspector panel. The panel docks to the right side of the window and contains two tabs: Terminal and Memo." = "点击工具栏右上角的 ⊟ 按钮可展开或收起检查器面板。该面板停靠在窗口右侧，包含两个标签页：终端和备忘。";
"Terminal Tab" = "终端标签页";
"An embedded zsh terminal that opens at the current project's directory. Use it to run shell commands, inspect files, or manage git — all without leaving the app." = "在当前项目目录下打开的内置 zsh 终端。你可用它运行 shell 命令、查看文件或管理 git — 全程无需离开应用。";
"Memo Tab" = "备忘标签页";
"A per-project rich text memo editor. Notes are auto-saved after a short pause and persist across sessions. Markdown formatting is supported." = "按项目划分的富文本备忘编辑器。停顿片刻后备忘会自动保存，并跨会话保留。支持 Markdown 格式。";
"Heading levels (# / ## / ###)" = "标题级别 (# / ## / ###)";
"Bold" = "加粗";
"Italic" = "斜体";
"Inline code" = "行内代码";
"Strikethrough" = "删除线";
"Unordered list (auto-continues on Return)" = "无序列表（按 Return 时自动延续）";
"Interactive Terminal Popup" = "交互式终端弹窗";
"Some slash commands (such as /config, /permissions, /model) open in a separate interactive terminal sheet. The popup runs the command automatically and closes when it exits." = "某些斜杠命令（例如 /config、/permissions、/model）会在单独的交互式终端面板中打开。弹窗会自动运行该命令，并在其退出时关闭。";
"The exit code is shown at the bottom — \"exit 0\" means the command completed successfully." = "退出代码显示在底部 — “exit 0”表示命令已成功完成。";

// GitHub Integration
"Click the GitHub Mark button at the top of the sidebar to open the GitHub panel. After connecting your GitHub account, your repositories are listed and can be added to Clarc with one click." = "点击侧边栏顶部的 GitHub 标志按钮可打开 GitHub 面板。连接 GitHub 账户后，你的仓库会列出，并可一键添加到 Clarc。";
"Adding a Repository" = "添加仓库";
"Search for a repository by name, then click Add. Clarc clones it automatically and opens it as a new project." = "按名称搜索仓库，然后点击添加。Clarc 会自动克隆它并将其作为新项目打开。";
"Private repository" = "私有仓库";
"Public repository" = "公开仓库";
"Already added to Clarc" = "已添加到 Clarc";

// Skill Marketplace
"Click the brain icon (🧠) in the toolbar to browse the MCP plugin catalog published on Anthropic's GitHub. Plugins can be filtered by category or searched by name, description, or author." = "点击工具栏中的大脑图标 (🧠) 可浏览发布在 Anthropic GitHub 上的 MCP 插件目录。可按类别筛选插件，或按名称、描述或作者搜索。";
"Installing Plugins" = "安装插件";
"Click a plugin to view its details, then press Install. An interactive terminal popup opens and runs the install command automatically." = "点击插件查看其详情，然后按下安装。交互式终端弹窗会打开并自动运行安装命令。";
"Not installed" = "未安装";
"Installing…" = "正在安装…";
"The catalog refreshes automatically every 5 minutes." = "目录每 5 分钟自动刷新一次。";

// Status Line
"What is the Status Line?" = "什么是状态栏？";
"A fixed information bar at the bottom of the chat area. It shows the current project path, model, rate limit usage, context window usage, and total response time at a glance." = "固定在对话区域底部的信息栏。它一目了然地显示当前项目路径、模型、用量限制、上下文窗口用量和总响应时间。";
"Displayed Items" = "显示项目";
"Items are shown left to right in the status line." = "状态栏中的项目按从左到右的顺序显示。";
"Project path — folder path of the currently selected project (home directory abbreviated as ~)" = "项目路径 — 当前所选项目的文件夹路径（主目录缩写为 ~）";
"Model — name of the Claude model in use for this session" = "模型 — 当前会话所使用的 Claude 模型名称";
"5h limit — API usage over the last 5 hours (bar + % + time until reset)" = "5h 限制 — 最近 5 小时的 API 用量（进度条 + % + 距重置剩余时间）";
"7d limit — API usage over the last 7 days (bar + % + time until reset)" = "7d 限制 — 最近 7 天的 API 用量（进度条 + % + 距重置剩余时间）";
"context — context window usage for the current session (bar + %)" = "context — 当前会话的上下文窗口用量（进度条 + %）";
"Total response time — cumulative time Claude spent generating responses in this session" = "总响应时间 — 本次会话中 Claude 生成响应所花费时间的累计值";
"Usage Colors" = "用量颜色";
"The bar graph and percentage change color based on usage level." = "进度条和百分比会根据用量级别改变颜色。";
"Below 70% — normal" = "低于 70% — 正常";
"70–89% — caution" = "70–89% — 注意";
"90% or above — critical" = "90% 及以上 — 危险";
"Usage data refreshes automatically after each response. If the initial fetch fails on launch, it retries once after 5 seconds." = "用量数据在每次响应后自动刷新。如果启动时首次获取失败，将在 5 秒后重试一次。";

// Permission Requests
"What are Permission Requests?" = "什么是权限请求？";
"Before Claude edits files or runs commands, it pauses and asks for your approval. A modal appears showing the tool name and its arguments." = "在 Claude 编辑文件或运行命令之前，它会暂停并请求你的批准。届时会弹出一个显示工具名称及其参数的模态框。";
"Approval Options" = "批准选项";
"Each permission request offers three choices." = "每个权限请求提供三种选择。";
"Approve this single action" = "仅批准这一次操作";
"Approve all future requests of this type for the current session" = "在当前会话内批准此类型的所有后续请求";
"Reject the action" = "拒绝该操作";
"If no action is taken, the request is automatically denied after 5 minutes. Press Return to Allow, or Escape to Deny." = "如果未做任何操作，请求将在 5 分钟后自动被拒绝。按 Return 允许，或按 Escape 拒绝。";
// Permission Mode sections
"Use the permission mode dropdown at the top of the chat to control how Claude requests approval before running actions." = "使用对话顶部的权限模式下拉菜单可控制 Claude 在执行操作前请求批准的方式。";
"Use the permission mode dropdown at the top of the chat to switch how Claude handles permissions." = "使用对话顶部的权限模式下拉菜单可切换 Claude 处理权限的方式。";
"Default — prompts for approval before file edits and commands" = "默认模式 — 在编辑文件和执行命令前请求批准";
"Auto-accepts file edits in the working directory (commands still require approval)" = "自动接受工作目录中的文件编辑（命令仍需批准）";
"Read-only — analyzes and plans without making edits" = "只读 — 在不进行编辑的情况下分析并制定计划";
"AI auto-approves safe operations, prompts only for risky ones (requires Max/Team/Enterprise/API plan + Sonnet/Opus 4.6+)" = "AI 自动批准安全操作，仅对有风险的操作请求批准（需要 Max/Team/Enterprise/API 套餐 + Sonnet/Opus 4.6+）";
"Skips all permission checks — use only in isolated environments" = "跳过所有权限检查 — 仅建议在隔离环境中使用";
"Skips all permission checks — writes to .git/.vscode/.claude directories still require approval" = "跳过所有权限检查 — 写入 .git/.vscode/.claude 目录仍需批准";
"Only enable Skip Permissions on projects you fully trust. Mode changes take effect from the next message." = "仅在你完全信任的项目上启用。模式更改将从下一条消息发送时生效。";
"Double-click" = "双击";

"Skip Permissions Mode" = "跳过权限模式";
"Toggle the shield icon at the top of the chat to auto-approve all permission requests. This speeds up tasks but also auto-executes potentially dangerous operations — use with caution." = "切换对话顶部的盾牌图标可自动批准所有权限请求。这能加快任务速度，但也会自动执行潜在危险的操作 — 请谨慎使用。";

