"Toggle checkbox" = "切换复选框";
"Insert link" = "插入链接";
"Underline" = "下划线";

// Inspector Panel reset buttons
"Reset Buttons" = "重置按钮";
"Each inspector tab has a reset button (the circular arrow at the top right of the panel)." = "每个检查器标签页都有一个重置按钮（面板右上角的环形箭头）。";
"Reset Terminal" = "重置终端";
"Clear Memo" = "清空备忘";
"Terminate the current shell and start a fresh zsh session" = "终止当前 shell 并启动一个全新的 zsh 会话";
"Erase the memo for the current project (cannot be undone)" = "删除当前项目的全部备忘（无法撤销）";

// Hidden files toggle
"Hidden Files" = "隐藏文件";
"Toggle the eye icon in the Files tab header to show or hide dotfiles (files starting with a period, such as .env or .gitignore)." = "切换文件标签页标题栏中的眼睛图标，可显示或隐藏以点（.）开头的文件（例如 .env 或 .gitignore）。";

// Git Status (updated)
"The Git status panel at the bottom of the sidebar shows changed-file counts and the current branch. Click the branch name to switch between local or remote branches." = "侧边栏底部的 Git 状态面板会显示更改的文件数量和当前分支。点击分支名称即可在本地或远程分支之间切换。";

// File & Image Attachments — Auto-Preview Settings
"Auto-Preview Settings" = "自动预览设置";
"By default, pasting certain content automatically creates a preview chip. You can toggle each category independently in Settings → Message." = "默认情况下，粘贴某些内容会自动创建预览标签。你可以在设置 → 消息中分别开关每个类别。";
"Show a preview chip when a URL is detected" = "检测到 URL 时显示预览标签。";
"Show a preview chip when a file path is detected" = "检测到文件路径时显示预览标签。";
"Show a preview chip when image data is detected" = "检测到图片数据时显示预览标签。";
"Convert long text (200+ characters) into an attachment chip" = "将长文本（200 字符以上）转换为附件标签。";

// Settings & Themes topic
"Settings & Themes" = "设置与主题";
"Opening Settings" = "打开设置";
"Choose Clarc → Settings from the menu bar or press ⌘, to open the Settings window. Settings are organized into four tabs: General, Message, Slash Commands, and Shortcuts." = "从菜单栏选择 Clarc → 设置，或按 ⌘, 打开设置窗口。设置分为四个标签页：通用、消息、斜杠命令和快捷按钮。";
"General Tab" = "通用标签页";
"The General tab configures session defaults. Changes apply to newly created sessions — existing sessions keep their current values." = "通用标签页用于配置会话默认值。更改适用于新创建的会话 — 现有会话会保留其当前值。";
"Accent color palette (Terracotta, Ocean, Forest, Lavender, Midnight, Amber)" = "强调色调色板（Terracotta、Ocean、Forest、Lavender、Midnight、Amber）";
"Adjust the font size for the app UI (sidebar, toolbars, labels)" = "调整应用界面（侧边栏、工具栏、标签）的字体大小。";
"Adjust the font size in the chat message area" = "调整对话消息区域的字体大小。";
"Claude model used when starting a new session" = "开始新会话时使用的 Claude 模型";
"Permission mode applied to new sessions" = "应用于新会话的权限模式";
"Reasoning effort applied to new sessions" = "应用于新会话的推理工作量";
"Show a system notification when a response completes while Clarc is in the background" = "当 Clarc 在后台时，响应完成会显示系统通知";
"Model, permission mode, and effort can also be overridden per session from the toolbar — the chosen value sticks to that session." = "模型、权限模式和工作量也可在工具栏中按会话单独更改 — 所选值仅对该会话生效。";
"Message Tab" = "消息标签页";
"The Message tab controls chat display and attachment behavior." = "消息标签页用于控制对话显示和附件行为。";
"Enable a focused chat layout that hides the project tab bar and sidebar controls — useful when you want to concentrate on a single conversation" = "启用专注的对话布局，隐藏项目标签栏和侧边栏控件 — 当你想专注于单个对话时很有用。";
"Automatically show a preview chip when a URL is pasted" = "粘贴 URL 时自动显示预览标签。";
"Automatically show a preview chip when a file path is pasted" = "粘贴文件路径时自动显示预览标签。";
"Automatically show a preview chip when image data is pasted" = "粘贴图片数据时自动显示预览标签。";
"Automatically convert long text (200+ characters) into an attachment chip when pasted" = "粘贴长文本（200 字符以上）时自动转换为附件标签。";
"Themes" = "主题";
"Clarc ships with six accent color themes. Preview each one directly from the theme picker — the whole app recolors live as you choose." = "Clarc 提供六种强调色主题。你可在主题选择器中直接预览每一种 — 选择时整个应用会即时变色。";
"Terracotta" = "Terracotta";
"Ocean" = "Ocean";
"Forest" = "Forest";
"Lavender" = "Lavender";
"Midnight" = "Midnight";
"Amber" = "Amber";
"Claude default — warm orange-red" = "Claude 默认 — 温暖的橙红色";
"Cool blue" = "清凉蓝";
"Deep green" = "深绿色";
"Soft purple" = "柔和紫";
"Dark indigo" = "深靛蓝";
"Warm yellow" = "暖黄色";
"Slash Commands & Shortcuts Tabs" = "斜杠命令与快捷按钮标签页";
"The Slash Commands tab manages built-in and custom commands — edit, enable/disable, add, or delete. JSON import/export covers custom commands only. The Shortcuts tab manages shortcut buttons with JSON import/export support." = "斜杠命令标签页用于管理内置和自定义命令 — 编辑、启用/禁用、添加或删除。JSON 导入/导出仅涵盖自定义命令。快捷按钮标签页用于管理快捷按钮，并支持 JSON 导入/导出。";
"Checking for Updates" = "检查更新";
"Open Clarc → Check for Updates… to run Sparkle's update check manually. Updates are also checked automatically on launch." = "打开 Clarc → 检查更新…可手动运行 Sparkle 的更新检查。启动时也会自动检查更新。";

// User Guide — Sessions & Chat additions
"While Claude is responding, the send button turns into a stop button — click it or press Escape to cancel." = "Claude 响应时，发送按钮会变为停止按钮——点击它或按 Escape 即可取消。";
"Thinking Traces" = "思考过程";
"When the model reasons before answering, its thinking appears in a collapsible block above the response. It expands automatically while Claude is thinking so you can follow along, then collapses once the answer begins. Click the header to expand or collapse it yourself." = "当模型在回答前进行推理时，其思考过程会以可折叠的区块显示在响应上方。Claude 思考时该区块会自动展开，便于你实时跟进，回答开始后则自动折叠。点击标题可手动展开或折叠。";
"Forking a Conversation" = "分支对话";
"Hover over any assistant message and click the branch icon to fork the conversation from that point. Clarc opens a new session with the history up to that message, leaves the original untouched, and switches to the new branch. Forked branches also appear in the external claude --resume picker." = "将鼠标悬停在任意助手消息上并点击分支图标，即可从该处分支对话。Clarc 会新建一个包含该消息之前历史记录的会话，保持原会话不变，并切换到新分支。分支后的会话也会出现在外部 claude --resume 选择列表中。";
"Completing & Selecting Sessions" = "完成与选择会话";
"Click the circle to the left of a session title to mark it complete; completed sessions appear dimmed with a strikethrough. Use the checkmark button in the Sessions header to hide or show completed sessions." = "点击会话标题左侧的圆圈即可将其标记为完成；已完成的会话会变暗并显示删除线。使用会话标题栏中的对勾按钮可隐藏或显示已完成的会话。";
"Add or remove a session from the selection" = "将会话加入或移出所选项";
"Select a range of sessions" = "选择一段范围内的会话";
"With multiple sessions selected, right-click to pin, complete, or delete them all at once." = "选中多个会话后，右键点击即可一次性置顶、完成或删除它们。";

/* Inspector Panel Layout */
"Panel Layout" = "面板布局";
"Choose where the memo and terminal panel is docked." = "选择备忘和终端面板的停靠位置。";
"Right" = "右侧";
"Bottom" = "底部";
"Show memo and terminal together" = "同时显示备忘和终端";
"Splits the panel in two. On the right they stack (memo on top); at the bottom they sit side by side (memo on the left)." = "将面板一分为二。停靠右侧时上下排列（备忘在上）；停靠底部时左右排列（备忘在左）。";
